            <note xml:id="foot.f2"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_8409.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Edward Parr</ref> and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_8410.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Moritz August Herrmann</ref> were East India merchants; Semper’s wife, <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_8411.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Anna Sophia Semper</ref>, was Moritz Herrmann’s sister.</note>
